  "texts": [
    "In CNN training, the fully connected layers employed a dropout rate of 0.3.",
    "Consequently, this prevented neuron co-adaptation, hence mitigating overfitting.",
    "Besides, an early stopping mechanism was set to track the validation loss, the patience parameter was defined as 10 epochs where, after that time, if performance does not change on the validation set, the training is stopped.",
    "This ensures that the model is tested with sufficient and independent test samples for its generalization capability by making the split of train-test sets 70 -30.",
    "Moreover, DWT inherently reduces noise and captures the key features in both the spatial and frequency domains, thus helping avoid overfitting due to the focus on details of interest."
  ],
